author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Francis ANDRE "Avoid exiting ofbiz when running in debug mode,i.e with -DDEBUG=true set on theJVM arguments" https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-4776
This is a patch for allowing to run OFBiz in debug mode,i.e with -DDEBUG=true on the JVM arguments, and avoid to exit from the process when a Error or a StartupException occurs.
